QuestData.Title: Anok'suten
QuestData.Description: Come closer, I am ... dying.$B$BI was sent here ... to slay these Nerubians, but Vandril didn't ... know that they have a leader.$B$B<The dying blood elf coughs up a good amount of blood.>$B$BYou must find and ... slay Anok'suten. Get help. She wanders around ... Suncrown Village.
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay Anok'suten and return to Arcanist Vandril at Tranquillien in the Ghostlands.
QuestData.CompletionText: A nerubian leader? None of the scouting missions reported anything about this Anok'suten!
QuestData.RewardText: I apologize for the shoddy intelligence, $c. Had I known of this Anok'suten ahead of time, I surely would have told you.$B$BWe're spread too thin and things are slipping through the cracks!
